snippet.title: DIRT 5 | Uproar Content Pack and Free Update | Out Now! | Xbox, PlayStation, PC
snippet.description:
🎮 DIRT 5 - OUT NOW on Xbox, PlayStation, Steam, Windows Store and Stadia! Play now - https://dirtgame.com/dirt5​ 

DIRT 5's Uproar Content Pack and FREE Update 4.00 are rolling out now for Xbox, PlayStation, Steam and Windows Store!

UPROAR CONTENT PACK
🔊 Four legendary DiRT Showdown cars
🔊 More Achievements/Trophies
🔊 25 new Career events
🔊 New sponsors
🔊 New liveries 
🔊 New customisation options 

FREE UPDATE 4.00
🔊 After Dark Playgrounds Update
🔊 Night-time Playgrounds
🔊 Private lobbies
🔊 New iconic liveries
🔊 Technical improvements

The Uproar Content Pack is FREE to all Amplified Edition or Year One Upgrade players! Available on digital stores for other players 🖐️ 
 
Patch notes | https://bit.ly/3534rmB​

🔴 Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/dirtgame...​ 

👾 Discord: https://discord.com/invite/BYGnqQB​ 

🐤 Twitter: https://twitter.com/DiRTGame​ 

📘 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/dirtgame​ 

📸 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dirtgame/​ 

👽 Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/dirtgame​
